alarms are used to trigger notifications from any metrics
various options
alarm states
  ok
  insufficient data
  alarm
period
  length of time in seconds to evaluate the metric
  high resolution custom metrics

--------------

Targets

Stop, terminate or recover instances
trigger ASG
send notification to SNS


---------------------

Composite alarms

Composite alarms are monitoring state of multiple other alarms
AND and OR conditions

--------------------------

Good to know

alarms can be created based on cloudwatch logs metrics filters
to test alarms and notifications set the alarm using CLI
